8731 - Commercial Physical and Biological Research Summary > SUGAR RESEARCH AUSTRALIA LIMITED is an Australian public company. Its operations cover commercial physical and biological research. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. SUGAR RESEARCH AUSTRALIA LIMITED is headquartered in Brisbane, Queensland. It is headed by chief executive officer Roslyn Baker. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.60 million. Its net profit totalled $1.13 million. SUGAR RESEARCH AUSTRALIA LIMITED forms part of the services industry sector.
